Who's News:
   Southam Elects Ardell
   President and Chief
Southam also said its chairman, Hugh Hallward, 65, will
retire in May. Ronald L. Cliff, 62, chairman of BC Gas Inc.
and a Southam director since 1984, will succeed Mr. Hallward.
In addition, David Galloway, 48, a Southam director and
co-chief executive of Torstar Corp., was named to the new
post of deputy chairman.